org.diylc.common
Enum EventType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<EventType>
      org.diylc.common.EventType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EventType>
public enum EventType
extends java.lang.Enum<EventType>

Enumerates all possible events between IPlugInPort and IPlugIn. Some events overlap so be careful which ones you subscribe for and how you process them.

Author:
Branislav Stojkovic

Enum Constant Detail

ZOOM_CHANGED

public static final EventType ZOOM_CHANGED
Called when zoom level changes. Typically only one parameter of type Double is passed with new zoom level.

PROJECT_LOADED

public static final EventType PROJECT_LOADED
Called when a new project is loaded. New Project is the first parameter. Boolean flag is the second parameter and it's true when new project is loaded, false when the same project has been either reloaded or loaded with undo/redo operations.

FILE_STATUS_CHANGED

public static final EventType FILE_STATUS_CHANGED
Called when either current file name or modified flag are changed. The first parameter is the current file name, the second one is a boolean modified flag.

SELECTION_RECT_CHANGED

public static final EventType SELECTION_RECT_CHANGED
Called when selection rectangle is changed. Object of type Rectangle is the only parameter and it contains the new selection rectangle.

SELECTION_CHANGED

public static final EventType SELECTION_CHANGED
Called when component selection is changed. New ComponentSelection is attached as a parameter.

REPAINT

public static final EventType REPAINT
Called when selection size changes, together with a Point2D object containing selection size (x = width, y = height). Size is expressed in the default measure (cm for metric, inches for imperial).

SLOT_CHANGED

public static final EventType SLOT_CHANGED
Called when new component slot has been changed. The only parameter is ComponentType and may be null.

PROJECT_MODIFIED

public static final EventType PROJECT_MODIFIED
Called when the current project has been modified. Two instances of Project are passed as parameters, one before and one after the change. The third parameter is a string containing change description.

AVAILABLE_CTRL_POINTS_CHANGED

public static final EventType AVAILABLE_CTRL_POINTS_CHANGED
Called when control points under the cursor are changed. A single parameter is passed, an instance of Map, Set> containing all the components and indices of their control points that are under the cursor.

MOUSE_MOVED

public static final EventType MOUSE_MOVED
Called when mouse cursor is moved. Point object is passed, containing the current cursor location (not taking zoom into account).

LAYER_STATE_CHANGED

public static final EventType LAYER_STATE_CHANGED
Called when a layer status is changed. The first parameter is a set of indices of locked layers. All layers not included are considered unlocked.

STATUS_MESSAGE_CHANGED

public static final EventType STATUS_MESSAGE_CHANGED
Called to update the status message. New status message is passed as a first parameter.
